event.description: Calltime loaded. Your balance is now £10.00. Thanks for topping up with O2.
O2: Welcome to Pay & Go. Every time you top up we'll text you a code. Enter it at o2.co.uk/surprises to claim a Surprise. Some are big, some small. Terms apply.
O2: You've now got 300 free UK text and unlimited internet to use this month. Remember to top up at least £10 by 26 May to get your free allowance next month.
O2: Now you're up and running, go to o2.co.uk/hello to check all your Pay & Go benefits and the many ways you can top-up. To stop texts, call 2220.
O2 Rewards: Get rewarded with 5% back on all your top-ups every 3 months. To join text REWARD to 50202 or call 313 free. To stop SMS call 2220.
O2: Welcome to O2 Rewards. You now get 5% back on your top ups every 3 months. After 6 months this goes to 10%. To see all the benefits go to o2.co.uk/rewards
O2: Remember to top up by £10.00 or more before 26 May to get your text and web allowance.
O2: To check your balance and how many minutes/texts you have left, text BALANCE to 20202.
O2: Texts, minutes, Bolt Ons. Find out what you've got left, anytime. Text BALANCE to 20202 free. To stop texts, call 2220.

Confirmed! Text 32665 (FBOOK) to set your status.
To switch off Facebook Texts, reply "stop".
SMS charges may apply.
